Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.characters

Class MessageCharacterParameters

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.characters.MessageCharacterParameters
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MessageCharacterParameters extends Object implements Serializable
This class contains all the different parameters used by each character. It is used to communicate with the it.polimi.ingsw.network.client. It has only getter and setter
